@Styles.Render("~/Content/smallBanner")

<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12" data-wow-delay="0.2s">
            <div class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" id="quote-carousel">
                <!-- Bottom Carousel Indicators -->
                <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                    <li data-target="#quote-carousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active">
                        <img class="img-responsive " src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uifaces/faces/twitter/brad_frost/128.jpg" alt="">
                    </li>
                    <li data-target="#quote-carousel" data-slide-to="1">
                        <img class="img-responsive" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uifaces/faces/twitter/rssems/128.jpg" alt="">
                    </li>
                    <li data-target="#quote-carousel" data-slide-to="2">
                        <img class="img-responsive" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uifaces/faces/twitter/adellecharles/128.jpg" alt="">
                    </li>
                </ol>
                <!-- Carousel Slides / Quotes -->
                <div class="carousel-inner text-center">
                    <!-- Quote 1 -->
                    <div class="item active">
                        <blockquote>
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2">
                                    <p>The dough for the crust was awesome! We had the Italian sausage pizza. The sausage was huge chunks and had the best flavor I've ever tasted in a sausage pizza. I like the fact that we can also take the pizza in with us to watch the movie.</p>
                                    <small>Marian Popescu</small>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </blockquote>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item">
                        <blockquote>
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2">
                                    <p>I love this place! I can have a pizza made just the way I want it and can enjoy it with a nice cold beer and a movie! My kids love the pizza. This is a great fmaily place. :)</p>
                                    <small>Dan Ionescu</small>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </blockquote>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item">
                        <blockquote>
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2">
                                    <p>I was supprised to see that grand cinema had opened a pizza joint and the differnt types of pizza they have to offer.... wild rice pizza for example i've never even heard of..they also have a margherita pizza! i'm pretty sure this is the only place in hinckley offering these.</p>
                                    <small>Sandra Minea</small>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </blockquote>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <a data-slide="prev" href="#quote-carousel" class="left carousel-control"><i class="fa fa-chevron-left"></i></a>
                <a data-slide="next" href="#quote-carousel" class="right carousel-control"><i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>